snippet.title: Ghost Town - Arcade Ghost Shooter - IAAPA 2012
snippet.description:
New and very appealing multi-player video arcade ticket redemption shooting game with attractive 3D cabinet graphics and exciting digital sound effects. 

PrimeTime Amusements is a global operator, seller and event renter of video arcade machines and simulators.

www.PrimeTimeAmusements.com
